text: Karma Chhoden (born 13 June 1966), is an archer who represented Bhutan internationally. Chhoden competed for Bhutan at the 1984 Summer Olympics held in Los Angeles in the individual event where she finished 46th.Sports Reference Profile ==References== Category:1966 births Category:Living people Category:Olympic archers of Bhutan Category:Archers at the 1984 Summer Olympics Category:Bhutanese female archers
